metadatas.description: Data to match from the gRPC request.

methodName.description: Method name to match from the request. If you specify a name, you must also specify a `service_name`.

port.description: The port number to match from the request.

prefix.description: Header value sent by the client must begin with the specified characters.

serviceName.description: Fully qualified domain name for the service to match from the request.
